{"text": " Let us start by meditating for one minute. In this practice, we bring our attention from a lot of objects surrounding us towards ourselves. This 60 seconds is like returning home, back to yourself. We begin in three, two, one. Attention, attention on your breathing body. Watch how the body is breathing, the breathing body. Watch your breath.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 2.0, "end": 6.14, "text": " Let us start by meditating for one minute.", "tokens": [50364, 961, 505, 722, 538, 46850, 337, 472, 3456, 13, 50854], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.24774856567382814, "compression_ratio": 1.2522522522522523, "no_speech_prob": 0.08046222478151321, "words": [{"word": " Let", "start": 2.0, "end": 3.0, "probability": 0.8861468434333801}, {"word": " us", "start": 3.0, "end": 3.12, "probability": 0.9813433289527893}, {"word": " start", "start": 3.12, "end": 3.46, "probability": 0.991014301776886}, {"word": " by", "start": 3.46, "end": 3.76, "probability": 0.9766243100166321}, {"word": " meditating", "start": 3.76, "end": 4.34, "probability": 0.9787299036979675}, {"word": " for", "start": 4.34, "end": 5.52, "probability": 0.9869130849838257}, {"word": " one", "start": 5.52, "end": 5.8, "probability": 0.762450098991394}, {"word": " minute.", "start": 5.8, "end": 6.14, "probability": 0.9943326711654663}]}, {"id": 1, "seek": 0, "start": 9.8, "end": 18.06, "text": " In this practice, we bring our attention from a lot of objects surrounding us towards", "tokens": [50854, 682, 341, 3124, 11, 321, 1565, 527, 3202, 490, 257, 688, 295, 6565, 11498, 505, 3030, 51294], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.24774856567382814, "compression_ratio": 1.2522522522522523, "no_speech_prob": 0.08046222478151321, "words": [{"word": " In", "start": 9.32, "end": 9.82, "probability": 0.9817253947257996}, {"word": " this", "start": 9.82, "end": 9.98, "probability": 0.9982137680053711}, {"word": " practice,", "start": 9.98, "end": 10.44, "probability": 0.9890212416648865